-- ScyllaDB FTS demo -- seed data (100 messages, with embeddings).
--
-- Precomputed and checked in -- do not edit by hand.
--
-- Holds the 26 deterministic "needle" + "database" scenario messages every
-- query in fts/scenarios.cql relies on, plus 74 filler messages, so the same
-- cqlsh-loadable dataset backs both the BM25 scenarios and the vector-search demo.
-- Each row carries its real all-MiniLM-L6-v2 embedding (384 floats), so no
-- embedding model is needed to seed.
--
-- message_id is deterministic, so re-applying is idempotent (same message_id ->
-- upsert).
--
-- Apply after 01_keyspace, 02_tables, and the track index (fts/03_index_fts or
-- vector/03_index_vector). The fulltext and vector indexes pick these rows up via
-- CDC within a few seconds of insertion.

USE chat;


